  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[发布命令]]></title>
    <link href="http://zimuziyu.com/15143882196495.html"/>
    <updated>2017-12-27T23:23:39+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://zimuziyu.com/15143882196495.html</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
<pre><code>echo &quot;# wuzimuws.github.io&quot; &gt;&gt; README.md
git init
git add .
git commit -m &quot;first commit&quot;
git remote add origin https://github.com/wuzimuws/wuzimuws.github.io.git
git push -u origin master
</code></pre>

<p>网址<br/>
wuzimuws.github.io</p>

<pre><code>git add --ignore-removal .
